IF GRAPPLING_HOOK HEALTH 1
REMOVE "Rope" 1 1 GRAPPLING_HOOK 2 3
END
IF GRAPPLING_HOOK HEALTH 2
TALK Edgar There, the rope's firmly attached
SET GRAPPLING_HOOK PROPERTY MENTAL 1
END
IF GRAPPLING_HOOK HEALTH 3
TALK Edgar I need to find some rope before I can fire it
SET GRAPPLING_HOOK PROPERTY HEALTH 1
END
IF GRAPPLING_HOOK HEALTH 0
TALK Edgar It's a Grappling Hook
TALK Edgar I could probably use it to form a bridge to the other side, but there's no rope
SET GRAPPLING_HOOK HEALTH 1
END
